---
layout: layouts/default.njk
title: Home
---

<section class="[ hero ] [ bg-dark ]">
  <img src="/img/hero/home.jpg" class="hero__background" alt="Office">
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="measure-short">
      <h1>{{ "Make better decisions where location matters." | i18n(locale) }}</h1>
      <p>{{ "Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Suspendisse iaculis nibh eu nisi gravida, et interdum metus rhoncus. Duis vestibulum dui magna, at laoreet nibh convallis non. Aliquam sit amet felis in velit pulvinar pretium ac nec erat." | i18n(locale) }}</p>

      <div class="button-group">
        <a href="#" class="button">{{ "View our products" | i18n(locale) }}</a>
        <a href="#" class="button button--outline">{{ "Read more about us" | i18n(locale) }}</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="wrapper">
  <div class="[ image-panel ] [ breakout-left ]">
    <div class="image-panel__content">
      <div class="pad-top-900 pad-bottom-900">
        <h2>{{ "When location matters, organisations turn to us first." | i18n(locale) }}</h2>
        <p>{{ "Since the day Geolytix came into being, we've been telling our customers where to go; how many stores, who to acquire, where to open and how to optimise home delivery and click & collect operations." | i18n(locale) }}</p>
        <p>{{ "Investing in stores and online is expensive. We'll help you spend your money wisely" | i18n(locale) }}</p>
        <a href="#" class="button button--outline">{{ "Read more about us" | i18n(locale) }}</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <img src="/img/home/about.jpg" class="image-panel__image" alt="The Team">
  </div>
</section>

<section class="bg-regular-gray pad-top-500 pad-bottom-500">
  <div class="wrapper">
    <ul class="[ stat-block-grid ] [ auto-grid ]">
      <li class="stat-block">
        <h2 class="stat-block__number">35</h2>
        <p class="stat-block__overview">Talented People</p>
      </li>
      <li class="stat-block">
        <h2 class="stat-block__number">8</h2>
        <p class="stat-block__overview">Offices</p>
      </li>
      <li class="stat-block">
        <h2 class="stat-block__number">1500</h2>
        <p class="stat-block__overview">Happy Customers</p>
      </li>
      <li class="stat-block">
        <h2 class="stat-block__number">753</h2>
        <p class="stat-block__overview">Stores Analysed</p>
      </li>
      <li class="stat-block">
        <h2 class="stat-block__number">10</h2>
        <p class="stat-block__overview">Countries</p>
      </li>
      <li class="stat-block">
        <h2 class="stat-block__number">30bn</h2>
        <p class="stat-block__overview">Mobile Pings</p>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="[ hex-background ] [ pad-top-900 pad-bottom-900 bg-dark color-primary-light ]">
  <canvas class="hex-background__canvas"></canvas>
  <script src="/js/components/hex-background.js" defer></script>

  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="text-align-center gap-bottom-800">
      <div class="measure-compact">
        <h2 class="eyebrow">{{ "What We Do" | i18n(locale) }}</h2>
        <h3 class="text-700">{{ "We help retailers make informed decisions" | i18n(locale) }}</h3>
        <p>{{ "Since the day Geolytix came into being, we've been telling our customers where to go; how many stores, who to acquire, where to open and how to optimise home delivery and click & collect operations." | i18n(locale) }}</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <ul class="auto-grid">
      <li class="grid-block">
        <img src="/img/icons/network.svg" alt="Network icon" class="grid-block__icon">
        <h3 class="grid-block__title">{{ "Network Strategy" | i18n(locale) }}</h3>
        <p>{{ "It’s never been more important for a retailer to understand how to optimise its store network. Whether you want to understand the potential number of stores you can open, how new formats will work together or how many stores you should close, given your growth in online sales, we can help." | i18n(locale) }}</p>
      </li>
      <li class="grid-block">
        <img src="/img/icons/location.svg" alt="Location icon" class="grid-block__icon">
        <h3 class="grid-block__title">{{ "Location Planning" | i18n(locale) }}</h3>
        <p>{{ "Many of us have worked as Location Planners for major retailers. Over the years we have had experience in all industries and the public sector across the world.  Whether you need to understand how much a new store will take, sales cannibalisation or your online and offline customer profiles we can help." | i18n(locale) }}</p>
      </li>
      <li class="grid-block">
        <img src="/img/icons/omnichannel.svg" alt="Omnichannel icon" class="grid-block__icon">
        <h3 class="grid-block__title">{{ "Omnichannel Retailing" | i18n(locale) }}</h3>
        <p>{{ "GEOLYTIX believe many businesses are missing a trick by not better combining their demographic, spatial and customer data. Whether its loyalty card, online, banking or mobility data we would love the opportunity to help you drive out more insight and get the right mix of Bricks and Clicks." | i18n(locale) }}</p>
      </li>
      <li class="grid-block">
        <img src="/img/icons/spatial.svg" alt="Spatial icon" class="grid-block__icon">
        <h3 class="grid-block__title">{{ "Spatial Modelling" | i18n(locale) }}</h3>
        <p>{{ "Spatial is different. GEOLYTIX understand when a simple scorecard will suffice, or when  a customised gravity model or machine learning techniques will drive added value. We understand businesses don’t just need a model, but a framework that will improve your processes & management reporting." | i18n(locale) }}</p>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="pad-top-900">
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="text-align-center gap-bottom-800">
      <div class="measure-compact">
        <h2 class="eyebrow">{{ "GeoData" | i18n(locale) }}</h2>
        <h3 class="text-700">{{ "Where people live, work, study and shop." | i18n(locale) }}</h3>
        <p>{{ "We create datasets across the globe to help with your network strategy and location based decisions." | i18n(locale) }}</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="wrapper wrapper--short">
    <div class="window">
      <div class="window__toolbar">
        <span class="window__toolbar-item"></span>
        <span class="window__toolbar-item"></span>
        <span class="window__toolbar-item"></span>
      </div>
      <div class="window__inner">
        {% include '../_includes/partials/geodata.njk' %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="bg-secondary color-secondary-dark pad-top-900">
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="text-align-center gap-bottom-800">
      <div class="measure-compact">
        <h2 class="eyebrow">{{ "MAPP" | i18n(locale) }}</h2>
        <h3 class="text-700">{{ "Spatial intelligence customised for you." | i18n(locale) }}</h3>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="auto-grid">
      <div>
        <h3 class="eyebrow">Overview</h3>
        <p>{{ "MAPP is our online market intelligence and mapping tool which allows anybody to use location data for business decision-making." | i18n(locale) }}</p>
        <p>{{ "It is designed in-house specifically for your needs, from the design, to the functionality, to the map style, we create innovative solutions which work for you." | i18n(locale) }}</p>
        <p>{{ "Visualise your stores, competitors, filter by performance and generate reports in a matter of seconds..." | i18n(locale) }}</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="eyebrow">Key Features</h3>
        <ul class="checklist">
          <li>{{ "Catchment analysis" | i18n(locale) }}</li>
          <li>{{ "Demographic reporting" | i18n(locale) }}</li>
          <li>{{ "Site feasibility assessments" | i18n(locale) }}</li>
          <li>{{ "Import & export data" | i18n(locale) }}</li>
          <li>{{ "User roles" | i18n(locale) }}</li>
          <li>{{ "Gap analysis & hotspots" | i18n(locale) }}</li>
          <li>{{ "Dashboards" | i18n(locale) }}</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="eyebrow">Key Benefits</h3>
        <ul class="checklist">
          <li>{{ "Simple & easy-to-use" | i18n(locale) }}</li>
          <li>{{ "Accessible anywhere" | i18n(locale) }}</li>
          <li>{{ "Secure" | i18n(locale) }}</li>
          <li>{{ "Customisable" | i18n(locale) }}</li>
          <li>{{ "Flexible mapping" | i18n(locale) }}</li>
          <li>{{ "Unlimited usage*" | i18n(locale) }}</li>
          <li>{{ "Our GeoData at your fingertips" | i18n(locale) }}</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="[ button-group ] [ text-align-center gap-top-600 gap-bottom-600 ]">
      <a href="#" class="button">{{ "View our products" | i18n(locale) }}</a>
      <a href="#" class="button button--outline">{{ "Read more about us" | i18n(locale) }}</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="wrapper wrapper--short">
    <div class="window">
      <div class="window__toolbar">
        <span class="window__toolbar-item"></span>
        <span class="window__toolbar-item"></span>
        <span class="window__toolbar-item"></span>
      </div>
      <div class="window__inner">
        {% include '../_includes/partials/geodata.njk' %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="pad-top-900 pad-bottom-900">
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="text-align-center gap-bottom-800">
      <div class="measure-compact">
        <h3 class="text-700">{{ "Our products create success stories." | i18n(locale) }}</h3>
        <p>{{ "We build close, on-going relationships with our customers and will become your trusted advisers." | i18n(locale) }}</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <ul class="carousel">
    {% for i in range(1, 10) %}
      <li>
        <div class="card">
          <img src="/img/stories/cover.jpg" class="card__cover" alt="Photo of John Lewis">
          <div class="card__inner">
            <img src="/img/stories/john-lewis.svg" class="card__logo" alt="John Lewis Logo">
            <p>Our job was to focus on the process, rather than the modelling which John Lewis carry out in-house.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>

  <script src="/js/vendor/tiny-slider.js" defer></script>
  <script src="/js/components/success-carousel.js" defer></script>

  <div class="wrapper wrapper--short">
    <div class="text-align-center gap-top-800">
      <h3 class="eyebrow color-primary-mid gap-bottom-600">{{ "Our customers also include:" | i18n(locale) }}</h3>

      <ul class="[ logo-grid ] [ auto-grid ]">
        {% for i in range(0, 16) %}
          <li><img src="/img/stories/john-lewis.svg" alt="Logo"></li>
        {% endfor %}
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>